Build dependencies:
* ivi-logging
* pelagicore-utils
* glibmm-2.4
* pulseaudio (can be disabled -DENABLE_PULSEGATEWAY=OFF)
* jansson

Runtime dependencies:
* LXC >= 0.9.0 (we pass full path to lxc-template to lxc-create not available in)
* Glibmm

On Ubuntu/Debian those dependencies can be installed with the following command-line:
sudo apt-get install libpulse-dev libjansson-dev libglibmm-2.4-dev lxc

Component test dependencies:
* py.test >= 2.5.2

